# Important: use first-party tracking before GA

Google Analytics integration is useful, but I would not rely on it first.

GA can report traffic sources, dimensions, metrics, and key-event-rate metrics through the Data API, but it adds setup friction and API complexity. ([Google for Developers][3])

Better first move:

